dorothy hope smith ( october 1 , 1895 – december 16 , 1955 ) is best known as the artist who drew the gerber baby.http://www.gerberlife.com/gl/view/gerber - baby/index.jsp   education she was born in hyattsville , maryland to lincoln b. and mary l. smith .

business & industry : dorothy hope smith ’s charcoal sketch of a baby is a trademark of this baby food company

